                <h2 class="title-main-page">Steps of deal</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row steps">
            <div class="col-md-4 wow fadeIn step step-1">
                <div class="step__title">
                    <h5>Negotiations / Tests / Basic recipe</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="step__info">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    First step is negotiations about most suitable machine and demonstration of working the machine with
                    customer's mass or we will provide basic recipe of mass
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 wow fadeIn step step-2">
                <div class="step__title">
                    <h5>Making contract / Starting manufacturing</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="step__info">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    Second step is making contract and starting to manufacturing equipment and forming roller according
                    shape of ending product according customer's request
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 wow fadeIn step step-3">
                <div class="step__title">
                    <h5>Final testing</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="step__info">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    Third step is test the machine with customer’s mass and forming roller produced according customer’s
                    request
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 wow fadeIn step step-4">
                <div class="step__title">
                    <h5>Shipping</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="step__info">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    Fourth step is delivery to customer’s factory. We can help to organize delivery by sky, sea or road
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 wow fadeIn step step-5">
                <div class="step__title">
                    <h5>Launch at customer factory / Teaching custome's staff</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="step__info">
                    <div class="step-number">5</div>
                    Five step is launch the machine at customer’s factory and teaching staff of customers to work with
                    equipment
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 wow fadeIn step step-6">
                <div class="step__title">
                    <h5>Warranty period</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="step__info">
                    <div class="step-number">6</div>
                    Six step is warranty service (include online service) and after warranty service
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
